'''2015年斯里蘭卡總統選舉'''於2015年1月8日進行投票。現任總統、[[统一人民自由联盟|统一人民自由联盟]]候選人[[马欣达·拉贾帕克萨|马欣达·拉贾帕克萨]]謀求第二次連任，<ref name=BBC201014>{{cite news|title=Sri Lanka calls early presidential elections|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-29693336|work=BBC News|date=20 October 2014|accessdate=2015-01-09|archive-date=2014-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141111031629/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-29693336|dead-url=no}}</ref>受到前衛生部長、以[[斯里兰卡统一国民党|斯里兰卡统一国民党]]為首的反對派聯盟候選人[[邁特里帕拉·西里塞納|邁特里帕拉·西里塞納]]挑戰。<ref name=BBC211114>{{cite news|title=Sri Lanka election: Health chief to challenge Rajapaksa|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-30144182|work=BBC News|date=21 November 2014|accessdate=2015-01-09|archive-date=2014-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141206133311/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-30144182|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Sri Lankan minister quits, to challenge Rajapaksa for presidency|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/11/21/us-sri-lanka-election-idUSKCN0J50W520141121|work=Reuters|date=21 November 2014|accessdate=2015-01-09|archive-date=2014-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141231053610/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/11/21/us-sri-lanka-election-idUSKCN0J50W520141121|dead-url=no}}</ref>

本次選舉共有19人參選，<ref name=ABC081214>{{cite news|last1=Mallawarachi|first1=Bharatha|title=19 Candidates Vie for Sri Lankan Presidency|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/19-candidates-race-sri-lankan-presidency-27436802|work=ABC News|agency=Associated Press|date=8 December 2014|accessdate=2015-05-13|archive-date=2014-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218133218/http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/19-candidates-race-sri-lankan-presidency-27436802|dead-url=no}}</ref>採取[[排序複選制|排序複選制]]，選民在選票上可選擇第一、第二和第三人選各一人。

西里塞納以51.28%的得票率撃敗得47.58%的拉賈帕克薩，當選為新一屆總統。<ref name=TG090115>{{cite news|last1=Ben|first1=Doherty|last2=Munk|first2=David|title=Sri Lanka election: president Mahinda Rajapaksa concedes defeat - live|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/jan/09/sri-lanka-election-president-mahinda-rajapaksa-concedes-defeat-live|work=The Guardian|date=9 January 2015|accessdate=2015-01-09|archive-date=2015-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109133536/http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/jan/09/sri-lanka-election-president-mahinda-rajapaksa-concedes-defeat-live|dead-url=no}}</ref>拉賈帕克薩承認落敗。

